1
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,000
[Episode 23: An Escape Can Also Be Painful]

2
00:01:13,799 --> 00:01:15,830
Ma'am, this one looks good.

3
00:01:15,830 --> 00:01:16,960
Okay.

4
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,052
Nan Xi.

5
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:29,360
Jessica, go and tidy up for her.

6
00:01:33,829 --> 00:01:35,144
But I'm hot.

7
00:01:35,144 --> 00:01:36,589
It's not good.

8
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:41,008
Darling, how can you wear this?

9
00:01:41,008 --> 00:01:42,145
What?

10
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:45,560
Jessica, go and buy her a red one.

11
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,319
It's about to start. Hurry up.

12
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:48,457
Okay.

13
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:51,200
Darling, a well-bred girl

14
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,400
never lifts the skirt to her thighs.

15
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,680
- Remember that, okay?
- Why does she do that?

16
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,079
But it's all women here.

17
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:58,669
Okay?

18
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:03,484
Okay.

19
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,285
Great.

20
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:09,284
Here, ma'am. Have a seat.

21
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,583
Let me give you a massage.

22
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,039
You're about to go on stage.

23
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:16,631
Relax.

24
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,800
Ren?

25
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,439
What a coincidence.

26
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:30,199
I thought you'd left.

27
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:32,444
I didn't expect to see you here.

28
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:34,719
You left in a hurry that day.

29
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:36,439
You changed your number,

30
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:37,840
and moved.

31
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:40,550
Then you started a group chat, sent an "essay"

32
00:02:40,550 --> 00:02:41,760
and asked us for money.

33
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,920
Oh, I thought you...

34
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,344
It's good that you're okay.

35
00:02:45,344 --> 00:02:47,960
Hey, you...

36
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,247
Are you okay?

37
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,840
I left in a hurry,

38
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:55,680
because I disliked dragging things out.

39
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,439
I changed my number, because I resigned,

40
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:59,280
but you kept calling about work.

41
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:03,400
I moved, because it made me sick to meet you.

42
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,080
As for "asked for money",

43
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:07,520
you call collecting one's own money "ask for"?

44
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,879
Where I'm from, we call that "debt collection".

45
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:11,000
Right?

46
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,108
Yes.

47
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:15,400
That's because you didn't hand over properly.

48
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:19,527
I called about your duties.

49
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:21,599
That's right.

50
00:03:21,599 --> 00:03:24,199
I did your duties.

51
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:27,354
So you did poorly after I left.

52
00:03:28,091 --> 00:03:30,240
Messy napkins.

53
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:32,200
Chipped bowls.

54
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,440
Even the wedding setup

55
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:36,936
was proposed by me before resigning.

56
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,919
I didn't expect you to stay

57
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:42,379
after doing it poorly.

58
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,850
- Ren.
- Ms. Ren.

59
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,400
Sorry, Ms. Ren.

60
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,090
I'll handle it right away.

61
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,560
It's about to start. Where are you going?

62
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,800
You won't believe whatever I say.

63
00:04:17,944 --> 00:04:19,274
Good luck.

64
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:20,980
Let's go.

65
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,759
You have good taste, ma'am.

66
00:04:26,759 --> 00:04:28,808
Pretty, isn't it?

67
00:04:28,808 --> 00:04:30,920
- Can you touch up my makeup?
- It fits you well.

68
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,959
It's beautiful.

69
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,240
Is this pressure okay?

70
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,439
Yes.

71
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:37,079
- Can anyone touch up my makeup?
- Anything looks pretty on you.

72
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:38,408
Nan Xi.

73
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,079
I wasn't speaking loudly.

74
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,520
You were chatting

75
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:44,811
and didn't hear me.

76
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:49,707
Ma'am, please calm down.

77
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,680
I'm sorry, Auntie.

78
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,086
I'll be careful.

79
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,959
That's right.

80
00:04:55,959 --> 00:04:58,592
Be a good girl, darling. Okay?

81
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,160
Ma'am, you're so kind.

82
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,319
Yes. You're such a good mom.

83
00:05:03,319 --> 00:05:05,160
I'm so jealous.

84
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,240
You're so gentle.

85
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,393
Yes.

86
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,704
Should I enter or not?

87
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,480
Enter

88
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,360
or not?

89
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,842
Enter?

90
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:28,115
What if she wants me?

91
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:30,959
But I'm already here.

92
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:32,370
Give it a shot.

93
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:58,188
Li Nan Xi... gets married so soon.

94
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,760
Yes.

95
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,840
She said she couldn't take off

96
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:05,472
a blinding diamond ring.

97
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:36,292
It's... only... an audition?

98
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:42,639
So, why... is it here?

99
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:44,839
Because it's a business trip.

100
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:46,224
We can start now.

101
00:06:46,224 --> 00:06:47,600
What?

102
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,217
Oh. Okay.

103
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,062
I'll do it myself.

104
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:56,036
Mrs. Lu, Ma'am--

105
00:06:56,036 --> 00:06:58,148
I'm Li Nan Xi!

106
00:07:03,388 --> 00:07:04,399
Mrs. Lu.

107
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:07,170
I'm Li Nan Xi! I'm Li Nan Xi!

108
00:07:17,528 --> 00:07:19,200
<i>Ma'am is calling you.</i>

109
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,439
Not ready yet.

110
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:21,920
She has princess syndrome again.

111
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,480
<i>I asked her. She told us to ignore her.</i>

112
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:26,199
<i>The makeup is done.
She'll enter on her own later.</i>

113
00:07:26,199 --> 00:07:28,633
Marrying such a good family,
why is she so pretentious?

114
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,225
I'm not happy.

115
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,920
<i>I'm not happy.</i>

116
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,273
<i>Where are you?</i>

117
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,759
Why is she leaving?

118
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:43,015
Leave me alone!

119
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:48,460
Li Nan Xi.

120
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,279
Are you angry?

121
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:56,522
A little.

122
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,291
A lot, actually.

123
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,559
What's with your eye makeup?

124
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:23,279
The mother controls the color of my underwear.

125
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:25,520
The son treats me like a dog.

126
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:27,120
They're all pigs!

127
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,559
Had I known this,

128
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:31,799
I'd choose painting instead of them!

129
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:34,480
At least I needn't wear red underwear.

130
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,737
I've never been so tasteless!

131
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:41,080
But it has happened.

132
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,080
If I...

133
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:44,874
If I escape,
my dad will surely find and catch me.

134
00:09:44,874 --> 00:09:45,880
I can't...

135
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,645
Did you get your marriage certificate?

136
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,880
His mom said I can only get it if I have a son.

137
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:52,280
So why not?

138
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:08,040
Why can't you even handle a hand towel?

139
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,200
I promoted you to supervisor.

140
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,037
Are you freeloading here?

141
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:15,600
Next, let's give a warm round of applause

142
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,200
to welcome the groom's mother,

143
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,840
renowned entrepreneur

144
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,604
Zhao Chun Yan.

145
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,023
Mom. Slowly.

146
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:35,040
What are you talking about?

147
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,320
It's her son's wedding.

148
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,200
Why is she flaunting?

149
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:40,480
Do you know why Lu Shang broke up with his ex?

150
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:42,120
Because his mom wasn't satisfied.

151
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,320
Soon after that,

152
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:45,919
she rushed him into an arranged marriage.

153
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:48,811
Now let's welcome the bride.

154
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:52,930
The bride is here.

155
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:34,640
<i>She said she couldn't take off</i>

156
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:36,146
<i>a blinding diamond ring.</i>

157
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:51,567
I need a red envelope.

158
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:57,040
You finished the wedding?

159
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,160
I'm doomed, I'm doomed!

160
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,840
You're so efficient.

161
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,180
I'm doomed!

162
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:02,440
What? What do you mean?

163
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,120
Hey, explain it.

164
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,520
- Get out of the way!
- Where are you going?

165
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:06,672
Where dad can't find me!

166
00:12:06,672 --> 00:12:07,879
Leaving this mess to others?

167
00:12:07,879 --> 00:12:09,720
Stop! Stop your princess syndrome.

168
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,840
I'm not a princess. How can I have it?

169
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,200
Your dad loves you and is rich.

170
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,759
You can explain to him.

171
00:12:14,759 --> 00:12:16,639
My dad loves me and is rich?

172
00:12:16,639 --> 00:12:17,700
He lives downtown alone,

173
00:12:17,700 --> 00:12:19,080
leaving mom and me in Nanwan.

174
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,955
Do you know why?

175
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:24,320
Because I'm illegitimate.

176
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,840
When I was little,

177
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,840
my mom and I lived in the countryside.

178
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,279
If he really loved me,

179
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,560
he should have strangled me

180
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:32,938
when I was born!

181
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:43,015
I'm... I'm sorry. I didn't know.

182
00:12:43,015 --> 00:12:44,759
I should be the one apologizing.

183
00:12:44,759 --> 00:12:47,620
I'm sorry. I'm a mistake since I was born.

184
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:50,759
I'm sorry. I always pretend to be popular.

185
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:52,440
I'm sorry. It's my fault.

186
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,640
But I'm throwing tantrums here.

187
00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:55,944
I even try to prove I'm a

188
00:12:55,944 --> 00:12:57,960
worthwhile daughter by an arranged marriage!

189
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,600
- She's so mad.
- But he dared not

190
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,214
even come to my wedding!

191
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:19,037
Miss, your online ride-hailing?

192
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,760
You can't go!

193
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:23,480
I messed everything up.

194
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,300
What else can I do?

195
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,433
Get out of my way!

196
00:13:29,639 --> 00:13:30,639
I had an audition today.

197
00:13:30,639 --> 00:13:31,639
So?

198
00:13:31,639 --> 00:13:33,480
Did you forget what you told me?

199
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,553
Go on,

200
00:13:34,553 --> 00:13:35,920
with hyaluronic acid injections,

201
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,080
learning acting,

202
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,120
- being criticized,
- Let's go.

203
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,600
and acting.

204
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,279
If one escapes because he is in pain,

205
00:13:43,279 --> 00:13:44,957
where can he go?

206
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:50,910
An escape can also be painful!

207
00:14:01,760 --> 00:14:03,362
Darn it!

208
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:16,459
I knew your Taiwanese accent was fake.

209
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:18,385
Get on.
